column6: UAE-based Hayel Saeed Anam Group is a diversified business conglomerate with investments in industrial, agricultural, trading and service sectors. It was founded in 1938 and is based in Dubai, UAE.

France-based CMA CGM is a container shipping company. Its remit includes hazardous cargo and container fleet management. It operates a network of container terminals and stevedores and provides inland transport solutions. CMA CGM was founded in 1978 and is based in Marseille, France.
